For Windows : 
Follow this : https://code.visualstudio.com/docs/java/java-tutorial : simply refer this section : Coding Pack for Java

public class test1 {
    public static void main(String[] args) {
        System.out.println("Hello, Rock");
        System.out.println("Goodbye, World");
    }
}


Compile using : javac test1.java
Then run using : java test1
